dad94da72bdbdb44cdfaa14383993c14d0274","tid":1922647,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:32:46.000Z","msg":"全民初選<br />\n<br />\n五大選區租借場地一個禮拜<br />\n本土 素人 泛民 大家監測大家<br />\n<br />\n最後邊幾個贏嘅話就出選<br />\n唔好再搞分化啦 唔係就玩完啦"},{"pid":"6ee9462b20f95f89c2809f7f4383955282cea56f","tid":1922647,"uid":16713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"好想要初選"},{"pid":"5731d2728d6578e8562cbd1bddd34ebe9cc083a2","tid":1922647,"uid":135169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba93c746a27ff583941778cdb6fd9ab0dcf7e72e","tid":1922647,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"快D搞掂決定<br />\n然後大家自己打返自己條戰線<br />\n屌你老母 我本身仲整合分析緊份人權報告<br />\n上到黎見到仲反對緊初選<br />\n搞到用成個鐘睇D論點出po"},{"pid":"e5f09dbc91e240b5fd2a27f2bb386a3e458924b6","tid":1922647,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:35:40.000Z","msg":"大家唔好咁自私<br />\n初選搞得好就真係完全反映緊民意要求要邊個選"},{"pid":"95f74bbc63c104aa02fb9a31f92c35e5c92560f5","tid":1922647,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:36:02.000Z","msg":"咁之後大家選同配票先會有個政治合法性"},{"pid":"3b052850099de9a0822faa2b3336a91b52bc38ce","tid":1922647,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:36:10.000Z","msg":"有初選既話<br />\n就無梁天琦黃毓民等落選議員係大氣電波既感沼同文宣"},{"pid":"2be3d1b23d577e3635e88cc12cbfc476b0d51ce3","tid":1922647,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b052850099de9a0822faa2b3336a91b52bc38ce","tid":1922647,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:36:10.000Z","msg":"有初選既話<br />\n就無梁天琦黃毓民等落選議員係大氣電波既感沼同文宣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"玩浪漫可以等贏左先慢慢玩<br />\n而家呢條線度一個都唔輸得<br />\n其他線都未有實際效果出到黎"},{"pid":"8b9bf3435e3ce4b1d2a55c17d497bf5c05